  <notes>
    This task is the Wave 1 → Wave 2 transition gate. After it passes, Wave 2 (Code Page + 3 entry surfaces) can start consuming the canonical wrappers.

    The 50 KB gzipped budget is approximate — engine (~10 KB), 4 source pickers (~8 KB combined), 3 wrappers (~3 KB combined), mode logic (~5 KB), sub-components (RecipientField, BodyEditor, AttachmentList, ComposerActionBar — ~15 KB combined) totals ~41 KB. Leaves headroom. If exceeded, audit for accidental heavy-dep imports.

    Per CLAUDE.md §11: Vite solutions use `npm install --legacy-peer-deps`, NOT `npm ci`.
  </notes>

